# valence categories
# lexall (smp,ps,tr): ps->PASS, tr->CAUS
# lexps (ps, tr*): tr->TR
# lextr (tr)
# lexri (rc and/or it but no as=smp)
#   True,rc,ps->RECP, True,rc,tr->RECP,CAUS
#   True,it,ps->RECP, True,it,tr->RECP,CAUS
